    "name": "StellarGrift",
    "steam_appid": 3269410,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269410/extras/04b51f702e803d39280c7a7f271cb7a7.webp?t=1731056825\" width=800 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are an Intergalactic Outlaw who has stumbled upon a drifting, abandoned Space-Cruiser. Seize the opportunity to explore and seek answers to the greatest secrets of the Cosmos!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the sinister Galactic Force constantly on your tail, you’ll find yourself on the edge between life and death. Scavenge  vast Extraterrestrial Planets, build up your defenses, gear up, and prepare for the inevitable clash with The Evil Force.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269410/extras/6a66cb3f6f808d3bc36ddcb30969be16.poster.avif?t=1731056825\" width=794 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269410/extras/6a66cb3f6f808d3bc36ddcb30969be16.webm?t=1731056825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269410/extras/6a66cb3f6f808d3bc36ddcb30969be16.mp4?t=1731056825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269410/extras/cbd1a07bb35ffee54cda0aa637acb2e6.webp?t=1731056825\" width=800 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your newly found Spaceship isn’t in great shape. To traverse the galaxy, you’ll need Antimatter Fuel. Collect resources and materials from strange Alien Planets, then build devices to help achieve your goal. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, scavenging is not an easy job, as you’ll need to solve puzzles, battle alien creatures, and withstand harsh environments along the way. Work together as a Team! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269410/extras/ca616fb008d2dc27652292b1958c8f3f.poster.avif?t=1731056825\" width=794 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269410/extras/ca616fb008d2dc27652292b1958c8f3f.webm?t=1731056825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269410/extras/ca616fb008d2dc27652292b1958c8f3f.mp4?t=1731056825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269410/extras/e2d6bb94f9fdd16bc946ba5541d24209.webp?t=1731056825\" width=800 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are multiple ways to obtain Antimatter. You can choose from various Dungeons and Mini-Games within the ship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Spacecraft is filled with creatures, booby traps, and other dangers, so there’s plenty of cleanup work to do. It can get pretty silly and tricky, as the dungeons are randomized, and you’ll never know what you’re getting  into.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269410/extras/b0ba1fc140922cbf95cfc9ab73ae48e6.poster.avif?t=1731056825\" width=796 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269410/extras/b0ba1fc140922cbf95cfc9ab73ae48e6.webm?t=1731056825\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269410/extras/b0ba1fc140922cbf95cfc9ab73ae48e6.mp4?t=1731056825\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269410/extras/65e11a45deb4091eeb40ea2708bebc55.webp?t=1731056825\" width=800 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whatever you decide to do first... looting other planets for resources, prioritizing fuel production, building up your base, or embarking on thrilling adventures hunting down exotic creatures... remember that the most important rule in the entire Universe is to Have Fun while doing it!</p>",
